OL,3,CCouncil to be split into two in major
OL,4,Cshake up
OL,6,FSurrey will be divided into two
OL,7,Funitary councils, it has been
OL,8,Fannounced, as the Government made its
OL,9,Ffirst major decision on local
OL,10,Fgovernment reorganisation.
OL,12,FIn a statement, local government
OL,13,Fminister Alison McGovern also
OL,14,Fconfirmed that Woking Borough Council
OL,15,Fwithin the county, which declared
OL,16,Feffective bankruptcy in 2023 with a
OL,17,Fhigh level of debt, will receive a
OL,18,F"repayment in principle" of #500
OL,19,Fmillion from the Government to
OL,20,Fstabilise its finances in preparation
OL,21,Ffor the structural changes.
