OL,3,CCouncil to be split into two in major
OL,4,Cshake up
OL,6,FCouncils in Surrey submitted two
OL,7,Fproposals for reorganisation.
OL,9,FSurrey County Council were joined by
OL,10,Ftwo districts ` Elmbridge and Mole
OL,11,FValley ` in pushing for two unitary
OL,12,Fcouncils, while the remaining nine
OL,13,Fdistricts proposed a three-unitary
OL,14,Farrangement. The unsuccessful bid was
OL,15,Fbacked by Woking as well as
OL,16,FSpelthorne, Runnymede and Guildford
OL,17,Fcouncils, which have also held
OL,18,Fsubstantial debt.
