OL,3,CCouncil to be split into two in major
OL,4,Cshake up
OL,6,FConfirming the decision by Communities
OL,7,FSecretary Steve Reed, Ms McGovern
OL,8,Fsaid: "In our judgment, although both
OL,9,Fproposals met the criteria, the
OL,10,Fproposal for two unitaries better
OL,11,Fmeets the criteria in the case of
OL,12,FSurrey.
OL,14,F"In particular, we believe it performs
OL,15,Fbetter against the second criterion,
OL,16,Fas it is more likely to be financially
OL,17,Fsustainable.
